Progress Report 7
4/26
Added new prefab call reactScoreCanvas and reactScoreHolder for Reaction Mode.
Added the script for the reactScoreHolder. It shows the current reaction time to the player after he hits the target.
The reactScoreHolder will be self destoryed after 1 second.
Edited the menu scene and connected all the scenes.

4/19
Added new prefab call scoreHolder for Challenge Mode.
Added the canvas for scoreHolder. I think the text object can only be destroyed if it is under a canvas.
Added the script for the scoreHolder. The score Holder will show "+1000" text when the player hits the target. The scoreHolder 
will spawn when the target gets destroyed. The scoreHolder will spawn the same position as the related target. 
The scoreHolder will be self destroyed after 0.5 second.

