Progress Report 6
4/12
Fixed the bug where if a player don't hit the target before next target spawns, two targets will stack together
which effects the total reaction time. Now the first target will self destroyed before second target spawns.
Fixed the "time" is not showing correctly because scripts are not linked properly.

4/7
Added the new target prefab for new scene "Reaction Mode."
Added the new scene called "Reaction Mode." In the mode, the player will need to hit the target as fast as
he can, then the time that he spent will be recorded. After 5 times, the average reaction time will be
calculated by totaltime / 5.
Added the new script call ReactionModeControl, it basically controls the whole scene, including buttons, UI,
and spawning targets.
Added the new script ReactionModeTarget, it record the time between spawn and destory, then send the time
to ReactionModeControl for the result calculation.

